Package org.societies.android.api.cis

Interface Summary
SocialContract.BaseSyncColumns These columns are privately used by sync adapters and should not be used by applications.
SocialContract.DBColumns Helper class for defining constants to use with services.
SocialContract.RecommendationColumns These columns can be used by services to set data related to how they want to recommend various data types to the user.
SocialContract.SyncColumns These columns are used by Sync Adapters to synchronize database content.
